headline: MarketAxess Announces Trading Volume Statistics for February 2025
summary: NEW YORK, March 06, 2025--MarketAxess Holdings Inc. (Nasdaq: MKTX), the operator of a leading electronic trading platform for fixed-income securities, today announced trading volume and preliminary variable transaction fees per million ("FPM") for February 2025.1
